rComments: Professeur très sympathique et extrêmement disponible pour ses élèves! Il a plus de facilité à s'exprimer en français qu'en anglais mais il se débrouille très bien quand même. Le cahier d'exercice est essentiel étant donné que la majorité des travaux / devoirs s'y trouvent.

Professor Da Silva is a very knowledgable and cool professor. He is actually a diplomat for the Embassy of Portugal. He is extremely energetic in class and tries his best to provide his students with all the learning tools he can. His English is not always 100 percent, but if anything you may learn a little portuegese out of it!
Totally cool, totally funny, and you'll learn a ton of stuff while actually enjoying it. Take him if you can, he's excellent!
